Package: SigAct
Type: Package
title: A package for tracking mutational signatures over time.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Xindi Zhang
Maintainer: Xindi Zhang <xindi.zhang@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: SigAct set up TrackSig, "a framework to infer
             mutational signatures over time", in R. It also
             improves TrackSig by aligning signature trajectories
             of multiple samples from the same patient and provide 
             detailed information for mutational signatures. See the
             git hub page for documents and examples.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: TRUE
